title: Distressed mono-spaced font
content:
Hi All,

I was hoping if anyone can ID this please? I've spent quite some time trying to Google an answer, but I'm drawing a blank.

Many thanks, Si

comments.content: The closest I have is [Typewriter a602](http://web.archive.org/web/20131014064947/http:/www.dafont.com/typewriter-a602.font) by Mr Fisk. A bit different but most probably a better quality: [FF Magda](http://web.archive.org/web/20131014064947/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/fontfont/ff-magda) (NOT Clean version)
Thanks Ryuk - Typewriter a602 looks the closest match... Case closed!
